description: Try our easy to follow Sushi-Style Wraps recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Wrap,Pescatarian,Fish,Tree nut free,Quick & easy lunch,Sesame free,Spinach,Peanut free
name: SushiStyle Wraps Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Trim edges of wraps to make them square.

Mix tuna with egg and cream cheese. Lay spinach evenly over wraps. Top with tuna mixture, avocado and carrot. Roll up firmly, like sushi. Cut each roll into pieces and put into a sealable container, or keep rolls whole and wrap in plastic.
